@node not28 "FREE CHOICE PPC KERNEL PETITION WEB PAGE"

FREE CHOICE @{B}PPC@{UB} KERNEL PETITION WEB PAGE
----------------------------------------

This   is   a   text  from  "Free  choice  @{B}PPC@{UB}  kernel  petition  Web  page"  on
@{B}jagor.srce.hr/~doozanic@{UB}

---
Free choice @{B}PPC@{UB} kernel petition Web page

It's up to @{B}Amiga@{UB} users to choose!

Since  it  is  obvious that @{B}Phase5@{UB} and @{B}Haage & Partner@{UB} can not make an agreement
between  themselfs  which can resolve the current @{B}PPC@{UB} kernel for @{B}Amiga@{UB} situation
it  is  time  for  @{B}Amiga@{UB}  users  to decide that for them. This page is not about
preferring  one  or another kernel (@{I}ppc.library@{UI} or @{B}WarpOS@{UB}), it is about giving a
@{B}PPC  Amiga@{UB}  user  the free choice to choose which one they want to use. With the
time  the  better @{B}PPC@{UB} kernel will win what will depend about number of available
@{B}PPC@{UB} programs and better particular kernel support and of course perfomance.

However,  to  archieve the equal conditions for both kernel to race against each
other  it  is important to remove @{I}ppc.library@{UI} from @{B}Blizzard PPC@{UB} flashrom. @{B}Phase5@{UB}
@{I}ppc.library@{UI}  is  loaded  all the time on @{B}BlizzardsPPC@{UB} and make a lot of problems
for @{B}Haage & Partner WarpOS@{UB} functioning correctly on these boards (it needs to be
terminated).

This  is  what this petition is all about... the free choice for @{B}Amiga PPC@{UB} users
to choose which one they want to use without forcing to one solution or another.
Right  now  @{I}ppc.library@{UI}  from  @{B}phase5@{UB}  is forcing user to use @{B}phase5@{UB} @{I}ppc.library@{UI}
kernel.  @{I}PPC.library@{UI}  can  be  placed  in  @{I}libs:@{UI}  and function correctly like it
already does on @{B}CyberStormPPC@{UB} cards.

If  you  want  that  @{I}ppc.library@{UI}  be  removed  from flashrom and placed in @{I}libs:@{UI}
instead,  sign  petition  (open  for  all  @{B}Amiga@{UB}  users,  not  just ones who own
@{B}BlizzardPPC@{UB}  card)  which  will  be sent to @{B}phase5@{UB} (Mr. @{I}Wolf Dietrich@{UI}) with this
content:


@{I}Mr. Wolf Dietrich,


With  this  petition, the @{B}Amiga@{UB} users ask to @{B}Phase5 GMBH@{UB} to move the ppc.library
of  the  @{B}BlizzardPPC@{UB} boards from the flashrom to the libs directory (like in the
@{B}CyberstormPPC@{UB}  boards). This will not disable ppc.library kernel in any way, but
it  will give to the users the freedom to choose which @{B}PPC@{UB} kernel to use. We all
hope in a Your positive reply to this issue.

